WEBVTT

00:00.333 --> 00:02.600
-You have one child together.
-Correct, Your Honor.

00:02.667 --> 00:05.233
You found a phone
his father had bought for him.

00:05.300 --> 00:08.667
This is what his mother said
she found on the phone.

00:08.734 --> 00:12.600
That's-that's disturbing.
That is disturbing, Your Honor.

00:12.667 --> 00:15.367
-[Judy] Yeah, it's disturbing.
-[sobs]

00:15.433 --> 00:17.834
It would be disturbing
to me as a parent.

00:17.900 --> 00:20.433
[narrator] <i>This is </i>Judy Justice.

00:20.500 --> 00:23.633
