-Thank you, Kevin.
-You're welcome.

00:56.834 --> 00:59.900
Mr. Kirkpatrick,
you and your wife, ex-wife,

00:59.967 --> 01:02.467
were married
for a short period of time,

01:02.533 --> 01:04.033
